maybe
--------------------------------------------------------

Assets Explore includes a popup with Public and Friends-only visibility.
The menu bar shows an asset counter and allows selecting a borrowing date range, while badges serve a separate purpose.

Assets can be filtered by date to display availability and capacity.
For events, fully booked items appear as Occupied. 
Each asset may have a price set in the Asset Editor, though the Explore route development is still undecided.

Occupancy for selected dates must be clearly visible in both the popup and item view.
Events also include an expense field with amount and currency.

